"""
FLOW LOCAL — Live Bilingual Interpreter (100% Local)
No cloud calls. Whisper + Ollama + Piper TTS on-device.

Pipeline:
  Browser mic → WebSocket → Silero VAD → faster-whisper → Ollama → Piper TTS → Browser

Same WebSocket protocol as server.py — browser client needs zero changes.

Hardened version:
  - Energy pre-filter (skip silence before Whisper)
  - Whisper hallucination guard
  - Max speech duration limit (prevents runaway segments)
  - Ollama timeout/retry
  - Echo suppression (mute mic during TTS playback)
  - Latency tracking per turn
"""

